title: Beautiful 5 Bedroom Home *For Lease*
posting_body: ['Vacant and ready for move-in!', 'Beautiful well-kept home.', 'Open floor plan with large kitchen overlooking family room and breakfast area.', 'Some amenities include separate formal dining, office, vaulted ceilings, stainless steel appliances, washer/dryer and refrigerator included, Granite counter tops, vegetable gardens, spacious covered patio, large open game room, huge master suite on main floor with separate garden tub and walk-in shower plus walk-in closet, island kitchen, garage door opener, full size laundry room on main level, spacious pantry, Round Rock Schools, close to Brushy Creek Park, white stone masonry with brick accents exterior, towering trees, subway glass tile backsplash, vented stainless steel vent hood, recess lights, 5 burner gas stove, tiled backsplash around bathtub/showers, tear drop lights and more.', 'Ask about our Lease Buyout Program & $2,000 Buyer Rebate Program!', 'For more details, call', 'show contact info', '<URL>', 'Listed by: Premiere Team Real Estate', '------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------', 'Price and availability may change at anytime without notice.', ' All information contained within should be considered reliable but cannot be guaranteed – nirav .', 'Premiere Team Real Estate Agents have been helping people buy, sell, rent and invest in homes for over 20 years throughout Austin, Downtown Austin, West Campus, University of Texas, Cedar Park, Georgetown, Hutto, Lago Vista, Lake Travis, Lakeway, Leander, Pflugerville, Round Rock, Texas and outlining areas in Travis and Williamson county.']
